snippet.title: The Bookwalker: Thief of Tales - Cinematic Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Your journey into fictional worlds of treachery and wonder begins on June 22nd! The Bookwalker: Thief of Tales is a narrative adventure with turn-based combat, puzzles and stunning top-down and first-person visuals! Coming to PlayStation®5 and PlayStation®4 on June 22nd, 2023.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
